latestIgtvVideos.title: Healthy Apple Cinnamon Cupcakes
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
FIRST TIME baking with Mirana & needless to say she’s going to be baking a lot more!! Our little MasterChef made the yummiest cupcakes with her mum-Me & loved eating them too😄❤️

Apple Cinnamon cupcake recipe (gluten free/sugar free) : 

Ingredients :
* 1 cup oats flour (I blended organic rolled oats)
* 1 ripe banana
* 1/4 cup applesauce 
* 1 egg
* 2-3 teaspoons maple syrup
* 1/2 teaspoon cinnamon
* 1/2 teaspoon baking soda
* 1/4 teaspoon pink salt
* Chopped apple pieces
* Chocolate chips (optional)

To bake : 
* Preheat oven to 350 degrees F/ 180 degrees C. Grease the tray with Olive oil. 
* In a blender, add in the oats, banana, applesauce, egg, maple syrup, baking soda, salt and cinnamon. Blend for 20 seconds on low, scrape down the sides of the blender. Blend until the batter is smooth in texture.
* Add in the apple chunks & chocolate chips on top. 
* Spoon the cupcake mixture into the tray.
* Bake for 15-20 minutes. Let it cool & serve. 

#babybaker #masterchef #healthyfood #glutenfree #minibaker #babygirl #momanddaughter #bestdays #healthycake #babychef

latestIgtvVideos.title: Easy Weight Loss tips
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I lost 30 kilos in 7.5 months post delivery. I had no time to workout but a healthy lifestyle and mostly a very healthy breakfast helped me shed all that pregnancy weight! 💪🏻

I dint follow any fad diet (no paleo❌ no keto❌). 

I ate carbs, sugar & everything I wanted to but of-course in limits. Avoid binge eating but never give up on your cravings! 

Few things I followed & still do : 
1) Intermittent fasting but only 12-14 hours (easier to follow & make it a lifestyle)

2) Oats topped with superfoods worked like magic! It makes me feel full for longer hours and reduces my daily calorie intake! 

3) Oats + 2 boiled eggs + a fruit + black coffee. This has been my only breakfast postpartum. I eat everything and anything I want to for lunch & dinner (carbs, fat & processed sugar included but in limited quantity).

4) EXTRA TIP : Drink atleast 3-4 liters of water everyday. It’ll help you shed the kilos faster & detox to get a healthy glow ♥️
